name: Supergirl (DC Comic)
description:
This is a lora for Supergirl outfit from my Patreon sub request.

You can check it out for custom Lora model.

lora wight of 0.6-0.7 gives a very good result. highres fix also helps.

this model is flexible with character while retaining the outfit.

I have 2 more models based on stable diffusion 1.5 and novel ai but they need more testing.

modelVersions.name: Supergirl
modelVersions.description:
based on anything v4.5

use Lora weight of 0.6-0.7
